{
  "stem": "21812.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He would be able to put the money-- which was supposed to have been repaid when I left, because what the money was meant for, passage, the final passage to-- passage to another country.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he would take me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The money must have gone to a Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a Jewish organization who took care of that whole project in England.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he deposited the money, and-- which wasn't-- as I think now, and I've thought for many years, was a totally amazing thing for a stranger to, to respond like that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for him-- and I knew it afterwards, it was very simple.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like so many of those people who had helped the Jews, that somebody appealed to you for help, and you had to respond.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no-- this was not a question of-- he didn't agonize over that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He did that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he did it on his own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't think his wife really supported him 100%, but he did it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was, he was a wonderful man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He came after the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He came to the United States, to visit us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Just to see how we were doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I wanted to repay him at that time, and he wouldn't take the money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "His-- one of his daughters is still alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She is 85, and I still call her and I'm in touch with her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So that's how I eventually got to England.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was not an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- this-- that was done even in Vienna through the Kindertransport organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was an organization in Vienna which worked with the, the British government, and the British organization in England.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we had nothing to do with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was handled by that organization.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took care of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
